  <hr>  <p><em>Dear </em></p>
  <p><em>We are continually grateful for your financial support during the year ended 31st March 2006. </em></p>
  <p><em>As some of you maybe aware, Youth for Christ Nationally is going through major changes and re-structuring. From being quite separate centers with individual local governing boards, to a nationwide mission order with one Nationwide board. YFC has redefined itself as a mission and has introduced a new leadership framework along with new values and practices. This will help move YFC forward as a dynamic youth mission, and recapture the edginess for which YFC has historically been known . </em></p>
  <p><em>As always the opportunities we face, remain beyond our ability to meet, and every gift helps us bridge that gap. It also gives further encouragement to our staff and volunteer teams who always give far beyond the call of duty in the time and effort they put in. </em></p>
